T1  - Portfolio Choice with Market Closure and Implications for Liquidity Premia
AU  - Dai, Min
AU  - Li, Peifan
AU  - Liu, Hong
AU  - Wang, Yajun
Y1  - 2015/05/15
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2016/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2014.2116
