T1  - Household Production and Asset Prices
AU  - Da, Zhi
AU  - Yang, Wei
AU  - Yun, Hayong
Y1  - 2015/06/24
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2016/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2014.2130
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2014.2130
T2  - Management Science
